cloud-architecture-diagram

title Artemis City Multi-Agent Operating System

External Request [icon: globe]

Kernel [icon: cpu, color: blue] {
  Task Router [icon: git-branch]
  Agent Ranking [icon: bar-chart-2]
}

Agent Registry [icon: database] {
  Agent Records [icon: users]
  Capability Matching [icon: search]
  Scoring System [icon: award]
}

Hebbian Learning [icon: activity, color: purple] {
  Weight Manager [icon: sliders]
  SQLite Backend [icon: database]
}

Sandbox System [icon: shield, color: red] {
  Tool Whitelist [icon: check-square]
  Permission Checks [icon: lock]
  Violation Logger [icon: alert-triangle]
}

Agents [icon: bot, color: green] {
  Artemis Agent [icon: terminal]
  Planner Agent [icon: calendar]
  CLI Agent [icon: command]
}

Memory Bus [icon: hard-drive, color: orange] {
  Coordinator [icon: layers]
  Obsidian Store [icon: file-text]
  Vector Store [icon: grid]
}

Governance [icon: clipboard, color: gray] {
  Approval Workflow [icon: git-pull-request]
  Rollback Manager [icon: rotate-ccw]
  Checkpoints [icon: save]
}

Monitoring [icon: eye] {
  Prometheus Metrics [icon: prometheus]
  Run Logger [icon: file]
}

// Main request flow
External Request > Kernel: incoming task
Kernel > Agent Registry: query candidates
Kernel > Hebbian Learning: get weights
Kernel > Sandbox System: verify permissions
Sandbox System > Agents: execute task

// Agent execution
Agents > Memory Bus: read/write memory

// Memory synchronization
Coordinator > Obsidian Store: sync write
Coordinator --> Vector Store: async propagation

// Learning feedback
Agents > Hebbian Learning: success/failure
Hebbian Learning --> Memory Bus: batch sync weights

// Governance
Governance > Kernel: policy updates
Rollback Manager > Checkpoints: store/restore

// Monitoring
Kernel --> Monitoring: telemetry
Memory Bus --> Monitoring: latency metrics
Sandbox System --> Monitoring: violation counts
Kernel < Agent Registry: ranked agents
Kernel < Hebbian Learning: weighted scores
Kernel < Agents: return results
